    v1 = 0.0

    tmp = wp.cos(wp.sin(tmp))
    v2 = ((wp.cos(tmp + 0.03) / wp.cos(v1 + 0.17)) + 0.59)
    v1 = ((wp.sin(v2 + 0.77) * (v0 + 0.70 / v0 + 0.09)) - 0.80)
    v1 = wp.cos(wp.sin(wp.exp(v1 + 0.95)))
    tmp = wp.cos((wp.exp(tmp + 0.64) + (v2 + 0.24 - v0 + 0.71)))
    v1 = wp.exp(0.33)
    data[tid] = v0
